Raul: &ldquo;We need to outsmart the market, we need to make the right signings, do the right sales, the coaching staff needs to prepare the games properly like they do. Hard work and outsmarting the market. That&rsquo;s the two, I would say, essences of success, if we want to be there.&rdquo;<br />
<br />
Vinai: &ldquo;We need to continue to look at our wage bill. We have got, and it&rsquo;s well-known, a large wage bill. That&rsquo;s a good thing. It demonstrates the financial muscle and the financial power of #AFC. It&rsquo;s important for us to be successful. We need to spend that money efficiently.&rdquo;
